title: Malcolm Douglas - Australia - Beyond The Kimberley Coast [1976]
description: Malcolm Douglas - 1x05 - Beyond The Kimberley Coast - 1976 Adventure / Travel / Documentary https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malcolm_Douglas_(documentary_maker) With a small group from a coastal tribe, Malcolm travels by open boat to Montgomery Reef and camps on the islands. An old man shows his grandson the ancient skills, hunting and cave painting. When Malcolm Douglas immersed himself within an Indigenous cultural landscape, he took lounge rooms full of Australian viewers with him.
